model.name: Luan2007 - Blood coagulation model combining previous models and platelet activation

body.p: Mathematical model combining previous models (Jones1994, Leipoldt1995, Kuhursky2001, Hockin2002) into one model with platelet activation.

body.pre: Case A: 0, 1, 2.5, 5 nM. Case B: 0 or 2.5 nM.
Case C and D: 0, 1 or 10 nM
